{"tid":11004,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"難以致信！竟然仲有人一件ZNE都無！😨😨","createTime":"2016-11-29T06:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T15:16:47.000Z","uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f79162742daea6e9f2143424cbddbe3191e93fd","tid":11004,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"今日秋季旅行😽<br />\n<br />\n我地成組人尋晚已經分工買哂料 各自拎返屋企<br />\n<br />\n今朝返到學校集合<br />\n<br />\n我地五人組有四個係著ZNE😝<br />\n<br />\n兩個皇馬兩個曼聯 得負責買炭個肥仔著Nike<br />\n<br />\n我地問佢做咩唔著zne 仲著wildrunner咁out😒😒<br />\n<br />\n佢竟然問返我地咩黎 佢愛隊車路士有無出過😓😓<br />\n<br />\n即刻唔想同佢玩了 叫佢自己一組<br />\n<br />\n竟然仲有人唔知咩係zne 有無咁out呀😂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上車時佢仲問我地包炭點算 <br />\n我話你拎去燒啦 我地問人借就得了😑😑"},{"pid":"4d4c135345eb8533b1943b27d94dbd61a4741110","tid":11004,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"ZNE係咩？"},{"pid":"efc9671b39386cae97ab54e3e7575f505791a4ed","tid":11004,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ZNE係咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你邊到鄉下😒<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅巴爾朗尼碧咸著用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/151646_c831f55a5f629563ff6fa515df89e74a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F151646_c831f55a5f629563ff6fa515df89e74a.jpg&h=49b875e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z55NV5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz55NV5f.jpg&h=b92c2a69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/151712_256b833d0801e76d085dc450faf66d80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F151712_256b833d0801e76d085dc450faf66d80.jpg&h=25c545c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8521E72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F